"title": "8807: profanity",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8807: profanity",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Behaviour which dishonours God's name or brings it into disrepute. It is often the result of idolatry, injustice or irreverence. Scripture strongly admonishes God's people to avoid it.</p>\n<h2>General warnings against profanity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:31-Lev22:33\">LEV 22:31–22:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:5-Lev21:6\">LEV 21:5–21:6</a></p>\n<h2>God's name profaned through idolatry</h2>\n<h3>Through child sacrifice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:21\">LEV 18:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:3\">LEV 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:29-Deut12:31\">DEU 12:29–12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:9-Deut18:13\">DEU 18:9–18:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:1-2Kgs16:4\">2KI 16:1–16:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:1-2Chr28:4\">2CH 28:1–28:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:16-2Kgs17:17\">2KI 17:16–17:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:1-2Kgs21:6\">2KI 21:1–21:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:1-2Chr33:6\">2CH 33:1–33:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:36-Ps106:39\">PSA 106:36–106:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:3-Isa57:5\">ISA 57:3–57:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:32-Jer32:35\">JER 32:32–32:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:20-Ezek16:22\">EZK 16:20–16:22</a></p>\n<h3>Through the worship of idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:39\">EZK 20:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:25-Jer44:28\">JER 44:25–44:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:31\">EZK 20:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:6-Ezek43:9\">EZK 43:6–43:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's name profaned through injustice and evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:10\">MAL 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:12-Jer34:16\">JER 34:12–34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6-Amos2:8\">AMO 2:6–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:7-Amos5:15\">AMO 5:7–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:6-Mic6:8\">MIC 6:6–6:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's name profaned through false swearing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:1-Jer5:2\">JER 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:33-Matt5:37\">MAT 5:33–5:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:12\">JAS 5:12</a></p>\n<h2>God's name profaned through blasphemy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:5-Isa52:6\">ISA 52:5–52:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:11\">DEU 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:10-Lev24:16\">LEV 24:10–24:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:23\">ISA 37:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:12\">2PE 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>God's name profaned through irreverence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:2\">LEV 22:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:26\">EZK 22:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:1-Zeph3:4\">ZEP 3:1–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6-Mal1:14\">MAL 1:6–1:14</a></p>\n<h2>God's name profaned in the sight of foreign nations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:7\">EZK 39:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:13-Ezek20:44\">EZK 20:13–20:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:16-Ezek36:23\">EZK 36:16–36:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:17-Rom2:24\">ROM 2:17–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:5\">ISA 52:5</a></p>\n<h2>Penalties for profanity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:1-Lev20:5\">LEV 20:1–20:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:25-Jer44:30\">JER 44:25–44:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:17-Ezek13:23\">EZK 13:17–13:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:24-Ezek21:27\">EZK 21:24–21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:1-Ezek39:8\">EZK 39:1–39:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:2-Amos4:13\">AMO 4:2–4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:14\">AMO 8:4–8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:7-Mal2:9\">MAL 2:7–2:9</a></p>",
